content: Tech leaders share their entrepreneurial journeys, plans for the future  St Pete Catalyst
description: Futurists and metaverse experts took center stage during the Synapse Summit in Tampa last week, sharing their own journeys in tech and the future of innovation in Florida.  This year, the keynote speakers for the Synapse Summit were Manny Medina, one of South Florida’s best-known serial tech entrepreneurs; Cathy Hackl, dubbed the "Godmother of the [...]
